#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing &plasma-desktop; and &kde; Applications"
msgstr "Namestitev &plasma-desktop; in &kde; Applications"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can install &kde; applications, including &plasma-desktop;, on a variety "
"of different platforms, ranging from smartphones and tablets to computers "
"running &Microsoft; &Windows;, &macOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD; or &Linux;. Binary "
"packages are available for many different platforms and distributions, or "
"advanced users may build the source code."
msgstr ""
"&kde; aplikacije, vključno z &plasma-desktop;, lahko namestite na različnih "
"platformah, od pametnih telefonov in tablic do računalnikov z operacijskim "
"sistemom &Microsoft; &Windows;, &MacOS;, &UNIX;, &BSD; ali &Linux;. Binarni "
"paketi so na voljo za veliko različnih platform in distribucij, napredni "
"uporabniki pa lahko zgradijo izvorno kodo."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Packages"
msgstr "Namestitev paketov"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hundreds of developers worldwide have done a lot of work to make it easy to "
"install &kde; onto a variety of different devices and platforms."
msgstr ""
"Na stotine razvijalcev po vsem svetu je opravilo veliko dela, da bi olajšali "
"namestitev &kde; na različne naprave in platforme."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Linux;"
msgstr "&Linux;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Nearly every &Linux; distribution provides binary packages for individual "
"applications and the &plasma-desktop; as a whole."
msgstr ""
"Skoraj vsaka &Linux; distribucija ponuja binarne pakete za posamezne "
"aplikacije in &plasma-desktop; kot celoto."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install an individual application, look for its name in your "
"distribution's package collection. To install one of the &plasma-"
"workspaces;, like &plasma-desktop;, look for a metapackage or package group, "
"typically <literal>plasma-desktop</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite namestiti posamezno aplikacijo, poiščite njeno ime v zbirki "
"paketov vaše distribucije. Če želite namestiti enega od &plasma-workspaces;, "
"kot je &plasma-desktop;, poiščite metapaket ali skupino paketov, običajno "
"<literal>plasma-desktop</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some applications may be installed together with other applications in a "
"combined package named after the &kde; package they are provided in. For "
"instance, &konqueror; might be found in the <literal>kde-baseapps</literal> "
"package."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere aplikacije je mogoče namestiti skupaj z drugimi aplikacijami v "
"kombiniranem paketu, poimenovanem po &kde; paketu, v katerem so na voljo. Na "
"primer &konqueror; lahko najdete v paketu <literal>kde-baseapps</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have trouble locating &kde; packages for your distribution, please "
"contact their support resources. Many distributions also have a team "
"dedicated to packaging applications by &kde; that can provide assistance "
"specific to them."
msgstr ""
"Če imate težave pri iskanju &kde; paketov za vašo distribucijo, se obrnite "
"na njihove vire podpore. Številne distribucije imajo tudi ekipo, posvečeno "
"pakiranju aplikacij s strani &kde; ki jim lahko pomoč specifično zanje."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Microsoft; &Windows;"
msgstr "&Microsoft; &Windows;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kde; on Windows Initiative provides binary packages of &kde; "
"applications for &Microsoft; &Windows;. They also provide a special "
"installer application that permits you to install individual applications or "
"groups and all necessary dependencies easily."
msgstr ""
"&kde; na Windows Initiative ponuja binarne pakete &kde; aplikacije za "
"&Microsoft; &Windows;. Ponujajo tudi posebno aplikacijo za namestitev, ki "
"vam omogoča enostavno namestitev posameznih aplikacij ali skupin in drugih "
"nujnih potrebnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on the initiative and to download the installer, visit "
"<ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Windows\">the KDE on Windows "
"Initiative</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o pobudi in prenos namestitvenega programa obiščite <ulink "
"url=\"https://community.kde.org/Windows\">KDE na Windows Initiative</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "&macOS;"
msgstr "&macOS;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Individual &kde; applications can be installed through several different "
"<quote>ports</quote> systems available for &macOS;. Several different &kde; "
"applications also provide their own binary builds for &macOS;."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne &kde; aplikacije je mogoče namestiti prek več različnih sistemov "
"<quote>vrat</quote>, ki so na voljo za &MacOS;. Več različnih &kde; "
"aplikacij nudi tudi lastne binarne izgradnje za &MacOS;."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, visit <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Mac"
"\">&kde; on &macOS;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij obiščite <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Mac"
"\">&kde; na &MacOS;</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "&BSD;"
msgstr "&BSD;"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most &BSD; distributions allows you to install &kde; applications and the "
"&plasma-desktop; through their <quote>ports</quote> system."
msgstr ""
"Večina &BSD; distribucij vam omogoča namestitev &kde; aplikacij in &plasma-"
"desktop; preko njihovega sistema <quote>vrat</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on installing ports, see your &BSD; distribution's "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o nameščanju vrat glejte distribucijsko dokumentacijo "
"vašega &BSD;."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mobile Devices"
msgstr "Mobilne naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<productname>Plasma Mobile</productname> is an exciting initiative to bring "
"a new &kde; experience to mobile devices like smartphones or tablets. Binary "
"releases are provided for several different devices."
msgstr ""
"<productname>Plasma Mobile</productname> je razburljiva pobuda za uvedbo "
"nove &kde; izkušnje na mobilnime naprave, kot so pametni telefoni ali "
"tablice. Binarne izdaje so na voljo za več različnih naprav."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, visit <ulink url=\"https://www.plasma-mobile.org/"
"\"><productname>Plasma Mobile</productname></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij obiščite <ulink url=\"https://www.plasma-mobile.org/sl/"
"\"><productname>Plasma Mobile</productname></ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Live Media"
msgstr "Mediji v živo"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several &Linux; and &BSD; distributions offer live media. This permits you "
"to try out the &plasma-desktop; without installing anything to your system. "
"All you have to do insert a CD or connect a USB drive and boot from it. If "
"you like what you see, most offer an option to install it to your hard drive."
msgstr ""
"Več &Linux; in &BSD; distribucij ponuja medije v živo. To vam omogoča, da "
"preizkusite &plasma-desktop; brez namestitve česarkoli na vaš sistem. Vse "
"kar morate storiti je, da vstavite CD ali priključite pogon USB in zaženete "
"z njega. Če vam je všeč, kar vidite, večina ponuja možnost namestitve na vaš "
"trdi disk."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\">a "
"list of distributions that offer the &kde; workspace and applications on "
"live media</ulink> on the &kde; website."
msgstr ""
"Obstaja <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/download/distributions.php\">seznam "
"distribucij, ki ponujajo &kde; delovni prostor in aplikacije na medijih v "
"živo</ulink> na &kde; spletni strani."

#. Tag: title
#: install.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Building from Source Code"
msgstr "Gradnja iz izvorne kode"

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For detailed information on how to compile and install &plasma-desktop; and "
"applications see <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Guidelines_and_HOWTOs/Build_from_source\">Build from source</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobne informacije o prevajanju in namestitvi &plasma-desktop; in "
"aplikacij si oglejte <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Guidelines_and_HOWTOs/Build_from_source\">Build from source</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &kde; software uses <command>cmake</command> you should have no "
"trouble compiling it. Should you run into problems please report them to the "
"&kde; mailing lists."
msgstr ""
"Ker &kde; programska oprema uporablja <command>cmake</command>, pri "
"prevajanju ne bi smeli imeti težav. Če naletite na težave, jih prijavite na "
"&kde; poštne sezname."

#. Tag: para
#: install.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The recommended tool to build Frameworks, &plasma-desktop; and all the other "
"applications is <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/kdesrc-build\">kdesrc-"
"build</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Priporočeno orodje za gradnjo ogrodij, &plasma-desktop; in vseh drugih "
"aplikacij je <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/kdesrc-build\">kdesrc-"
"build</ulink>"
